{
  "text": "The past few decades has seen increasing studies in isokinetic muscle strength and endurance in various sporting fields such as swimming, baseball, water polo and volleyball [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] ; however, to the best of our knowledge, there has been no such specific study in archery.",
